<lb n="0491b26" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0491024" n="0491024"/>佛說呪小兒<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0491025" n="0491025"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0491025" n="0491025"/><anchor xml:id="beg0491025" n="0491025"/>經<anchor xml:id="end0491025"/></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0491b27" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0491b28" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0491b2801">「羅那多羅　摩羅提離　耽波羅提利　吼樓
<lb n="0491b29" ed="T"/>壽　無樓壽　聞闍　輂叉輂差」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0491b2911" cb:place="inline">「南無佛，南
<pb n="0491c" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1329.0491c"/>
<lb n="0491c01" ed="T"/>無法，南無比丘僧，南無過去七佛，南無諸佛，南
<lb n="0491c02" ed="T"/>無諸佛弟子，令我所呪即從如願。」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0491c0214" cb:place="inline">若小兒
<lb n="0491c03" ed="T"/>頭痛、腹痛，當說七<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0491026" n="0491026"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0491026" n="0491026"/><anchor xml:id="beg0491026" n="0491026"/>過<anchor xml:id="end0491026"/>即愈。</p>
<lb n="0491c04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說呪小兒經</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body>
